<h3>Foreground+Background Design Space</h3>

<p>The pivot of this project, at least in the conceptual level, is the realization that the relationship between the phone and the watch fits in Buxton&#39;s foreground vs. background interaction framework. Because it is impossible for human users to interact with more than one device at a given time, some (or all) of these devices must stay in the background. This gives rise to a nice 2x2 design space that actually makes sense. It explains where our vision is currently narrowed, what and where&nbsp;this project is exploring, and collectively what the big picture of Duet looks like.</p>

